high_descs: Turn right to exit the room and walk to the cabinet under the TV on the left of the tvstand.
Pick up the spoon from the top of the cabinet.
Turn left to walk into the bathroom and reach the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink and take it out.
Move to the left to face the sink.
Put the spoon on top left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed spoon on top of the sink.

high_descs: Walk into the living room, make a right to the tvstand.
Pick up the spoon that is on top of the entertainment center.
Take the spoon with you to the sink.
Put the spoon in the bathroom sink and wash it, then remove it.
Put the spoon back into the sink.
anns.task_desc: taking a spoon from the sink to another room.

high_descs: Take the spoon in the tv stand
Put the spoon in the sink, clean it off
Place the spoon on the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the spoon in the table clean the spoon place the spoon on the sink
